295
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:51,770
He just didn't want to marry me.

296
00:19:51,770 --> 00:19:56,940
Because when we broke up, everyone around me said...

297
00:19:56,940 --> 00:20:00,190
Hey, Jung Hyun Oh is seeing someone else, right?

298
00:20:00,190 --> 00:20:01,870
No.

299
00:20:01,870 --> 00:20:06,000
