311
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:46,030
What should we do? We should break up. Don't you think?

312
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:47,580
Right.

313
00:20:48,650 --> 00:20:50,330
Realistically.

314
00:20:50,330 --> 00:20:52,350
That's what I'm saying.

315
00:20:58,060 --> 00:21:00,940
Dear viewers,

316
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:05,020
that is how...

317
00:21:07,370 --> 00:21:10,070
I became a fool.

