383
00:26:06,650 --> 00:26:08,550
When she shows up,

384
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:12,390
I'll treat her really well.

385
00:26:13,590 --> 00:26:15,670
That's how...

386
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:18,640
I'm going to win her over.

387
00:26:20,020 --> 00:26:21,800
Because...

388
00:26:23,250 --> 00:26:25,640
I have one heart.

389
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:29,150
My heart...

390
00:26:30,050 --> 00:26:32,800
