391
00:26:35,810 --> 00:26:37,650
Wow, why don't I get any of that?

392
00:26:37,650 --> 00:26:40,140
No matter how bad the disease is,

393
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:45,200
I don't think that's going to change, Hye Yeon.

394
00:26:48,210 --> 00:26:49,870
So, Sunbae.

